{"tid":764741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（連登仔質素低撚到）屌你老母阻人打交都俾人批鬥","createTime":"2018-08-02T08:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T01:57:14.000Z","uid":51200,"like":26,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e24ec053413ff514636696b42992504845f52992","tid":764741,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T08:17:11.000Z","msg":"正話個Po真係痴撚線<br />\n屌你老母阻人打交都俾人批鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n花衫就算真係俾人打先，<br />\n之後d動作都過哂火啦，keep住一巴巴中落去白衫度<br />\n唔拉撚住花衫唔通拉住白衫俾人打咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nChild登真係child登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又唔係兩個大隻佬拎架餐隻抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女人打交唔勸得？打到其他人點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冷眼旁觀同大陸班生番有咩分別？呢度係百度定乜鳩大陸論壇？<br />\n<br />\n四眼仔我撐硬你攞好市民獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港d瘦撚child登仔唔洗理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ae177b715e56219c15993d0558e8fb85cc6dfb","tid":764741,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-02T08:17:57.000Z","msg":"補Link:<br />\n四眼仔見義勇為阻人打架片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/truthfulness19/videos/2038353239517187/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftruthfulness19%2Fvideos%2F2038353239517187%2F&d=2GwWNziinMHcMOHUFayb0v9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=ce864